page.title: 19My Family And Pet's
page.content: We used to live in Essex.When we moved to Reepham I was not sure whether I would like living here.We used to have some cats but we have'nt got them now. We have got twentyfive fish and a hampster called Poppy.She is a golden colour and I like her alot.My grandma has got a pet dog called Mandy and she is very good.My grandma live's just up the road from us.My mum is a Training Officer at County Hall.My brother goes to Wymondham College which is a bording school.We don't live very far from the school so I don't have to walk very far.We have got a climbing frame in our back garden.I like going swimming at the leisure centre and I like going to the Brewery to have lunch and a drink of Coca Cola.Then come home and watch television.I also like playing games.On friday's I play basket ball.
